rated by a computer system and does not require any physical or digital signatures.</p><h4>APPLICATION AND TERMS &amp; CONDITIONS FOR BUSINESS/ FRANCHISE WITH ACHANUMBER.COM</h4><p>I am interested to take a franchise namely "CITY POINT/A.N SHOPEE/GOLD SHOPEE/SILVER SHOPEE or any other tital name shopee/franchise" of your company. I have read and understood all the terms and conditions to operate the website and franchise. I agreed and abide the same. I accept that the goods received by me in the name of customer will be the property of website/customer in all manner. I don't have a right to see/open the goods of customer. I don't have a right to sell it to other customer. I will not mislead/deliver the wrong information to the customer which will be harmful for the website services/products/reputation. If i found in situation to deliver/sell wrong information and goods which are in the name of any customer to another customer, my franchise will be stand terminated with immediate effect and i will be liable to pay fine or compensation to the website. In this event the website have the right to forfeit all the benefits of the franchise. I will return all the goods/materials received by me to the website on my expenses. I will not use website name/logo/advertisement material in any form in my office/shop.</p><ol><li>I/We shall be treated as Franchise and shall Setup a shop/office to undertake the assignment torender services for the establisment/create and promotion of franchise network as City Point Franchise (applied for) with effect from the date of approval.</li><li>I/We are providing the information given on the prescribed format and this information is correct in all manners in my knowledge and belief. If any information found wrong at any time during the business, the franchise relation will be terminate at the sole discretion of Achanumber.com without any prior notice and I/We shall be fully liable for all the consequences after the said termination.</li><li>I/